1. I am a friend. 2. He is a friend. 3. She is a friend. 4. You are a doctor. 5. She
is a mother. 6. He is a father. 7. The book is black. 8. The banana is sweet. 9. The
bananas are sweet. 10. You are a good boy. 11. My pen is red. 12. My pens are red.
13. Her cat is big. 14. Brest is a big city. 15. My flat is in London. 16. My mother
is in the shop. 17. My book is on the table. 18. Her father is at home. 19. Our
grandmother is at home. 20. Her brother is at home. 21. The trees are green.
22. The tree is green.
